  "name": "Finance - Bad Debtor Process",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"finance-bad-debtor-process\">Finance - Bad Debtor Process</h1>\n<h1 data-id=\"financial-summary-report\">Financial Summary Report</h1>\n<p>The Financial Summary is used to perform an <strong>account level </strong>verification of data imported from Retail Express to your accounting package. In this report, transactions are broken down by:</p>\n<ul><li>Income</li><li>Payment Method</li><li>Sales (type of sales, both taxable and tax-free)</li><li>Freight</li><li>Gift Vouchers</li><li>Laybys</li><li>Accounts Receivable Movement</li><li>Inventory Movement</li><li>Purchases</li><li>Direct Costs</li><li>Duty</li><li>Surcharges</li></ul><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fress.zendesk.com%2Fhc%2Farticle_attachments%2F360001759996%2Freports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png\"><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001759996/reports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png\" alt=\"reports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001759996/reports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001759996/reports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001759996/reports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001759996/reports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001759996/reports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001759996/reports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001759996/reports_financialsummaryreport_resultstab.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/>Click to enlarge</a></p>\n<hr></hr><h2 data-id=\"using-the-financial-summary-report\">Using the Financial Summary Report</h2>\n<p>To access the Financial Summary Report:</p>\n<ol><li>Open Retail Express</li><li>Navigate to <strong>Reports &gt; Accounting Reports &gt; Financial Summary Report </strong><br/></li><li>Select from the <strong>Filters </strong>as required (see below for a detailed explanation)</li><li>Click <strong>Search</strong><br/></li></ol><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fress.zendesk.com%2Fhc%2Farticle_attachments%2F360001754936%2Freports_financialsummaryreport.png\"><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001754936/reports_financialsummaryreport.png\" alt=\"reports_financialsummaryreport.png\" width=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: auto; width: 800px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001754936/reports_financialsummaryreport.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001754936/reports_financialsummaryreport.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001754936/reports_financialsummaryreport.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001754936/reports_financialsummaryreport.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001754936/reports_financialsummaryreport.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001754936/reports_financialsummaryreport.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360001754936/reports_financialsummaryreport.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/>Click to enlarge</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#Top\">Return to Top</a></p>\n<hr></hr><h2 data-id=\"filters\">Filters</h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><strong>Filter</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><strong>Details</strong></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">Date From/Date To</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p>The date the transaction applies to your accounts. These are inclusive dates, meaning if you select from 15/01/2019 it will include transactions on those dates</p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>If you entered a payment on the 1st of July, but backdated the payment to the 30th of June, the payment will appear on this report on the 30th of June.</p>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">Accounting Method</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">Only the Accrual Method is supported - you will need to confirm this method with your bookkeeper or accountant.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">Country</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">Used to limit the report to locations within that Country only. Countries are configured via <strong>Settings &gt; Locations/Outlets &gt; Countries</strong><br/></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">Store Type</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">A categorisation method used to separate your individual outlets. Refer to the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Store-Types\">Outlets - Store Types</a> article for more information</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">Outlet</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\">The individual Outlets in the database</td></tr></tbody></table><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#Top\">Return to Top</a></p>\n<hr></hr><h2 data-id=\"troubleshooting-discrepancies\">Troubleshooting Discrepancies</h2>\n<p>If you've found discrepancies, use the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Accounting-Reports-Overview\">Accounting Reports </a>for a detailed review of transactions and to assist with reconciliation.</p>\n<table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Accounts-Receivable-Balance-Report\">Accounts Receivable Balances Report</a></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Accounts-Receivable-Movement-Report\">Accounts Receivable Movement Report</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/End-Of-Day-Report\">End of Day Report</a></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Financial-Summary-Report\">Financial Summary Report</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Fulfilled-Sales-Report\">Fulfilled Sales Report</a></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Income-Report\">Income Report</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Layby-Balances-Report\">Layby Balances Report</a></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Layby-Movement-Report\">Layby Movement Report</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/1Purchase-Order-Report\">Purchase Order Report</a></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Reports-Stock-Adjustment-Summary-Report\">Stock Adjustment Summary Report</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Stock-Adjustment-Detail-Report\">Stock Adjustment Detail Report</a></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Reports-Transfers-Report-for-Accounting-Reconciliations\">Transfers Report</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Reports-Voucher-Creation-Report\">Voucher Creation Report</a></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Reports-Surcharges-Report\">Surcharges Report</a></td></tr></tbody></table><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#Top\">Return to Top</a></p>",
